      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've been looking through some of the logs and i'm seeing a handful of different stack traces appearing, but none of them are super obvious. it's not just one single object and it's not all coming from one place. it feels like it's spreading across different modules. how do i tell if these are actually related or if i'm just seeing noise?",
